ref=\"http://hudsonvalleyhost.com/aboutus.php\">several awards</a> over the past few years. Cpanel can be added for an additional $15/Month. As usual, we suggest you read their <a href=\"http://www.hudsonvalleyhost.com/tos.php\">Terms of Service</a> before purchasing.</p><p><strong>Network Information:</strong></p><p><u>Dallas, TX</u>: 198.23.135.130 | <a href=\"http://198.23.135.130/test100.bin\">http://198.23.135.130/test100.bin</a><br>\n<u>New York</u>: 198.23.157.172 | <a href=\"http://198.23.157.172/test100.bin\">http://198.23.157.172/test100.bin</a><br>\n<u>Los Angeles</u>: 192.210.195.194 | <a href=\"http://192.210.195.194/test100.bin\">http://192.210.195.194/test100.bin</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhudsonvalleyhost-15year-128mb-openvz-in-buffalo-dallas-and-los-angeles%2F&amp;t=HudsonValleyHost%20-%20%2415%2FYear%20128MB%20OpenVZ%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20Dallas%20and%20Los%20Angeles\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=HudsonValleyHost%20-%20%2415%2FYear%20128MB%20OpenVZ%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20Dallas%20and%20Los%20Angeles&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhudsonvalleyhost-15year-128mb-openvz-in-buffalo-dallas-and-los-angeles%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><sp